Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:15.89,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弾む鼓動とジャンプしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.97,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}軽やかなスピードで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:22.51,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日だって突き抜けちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:27.61,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心変わりもご愛嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:30.63,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せのアンテナは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:34.16,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一つじゃ足りないです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:39.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}七色ツバサ広げて　願いを届けに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:47.42,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔の磁石　ハートにぎゅっと　急がなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうだっ！ハチャメチャ元気に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ハッピー集めちゃいましょ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:19:00.49,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真面目じめじめ悩んでないで　カラッと笑い飛ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:06.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ぐっと↑ポジティブシンキング　絶対カラフル宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:10.12,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}志を打ち上げろ　GO GO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:15.09,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来ロケット駆けてく　追いつけ追い越せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:15.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}情绪激动地跳了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.97,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这轻快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:22.51,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛能穿越明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:27.61,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}改变心意也有可爱之处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:30.63,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸福的天线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:34.16,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}岂能只有唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:39.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开七色翅膀  去传达愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:47.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欢笑的磁铁  揪紧内心  必须加快速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}没错！  用不可思议的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}来收集幸福！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:19:00.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要认真地在那烦恼纠结  爽朗地一笑而过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:06.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}GOOD↑积极思考  绝对绚丽多彩的宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:10.12,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}表露志向  GO GO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:15.09,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冲向未来的火箭  追上去赶超吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪了  明明放在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了冬马？  出什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树  看到我的布丁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明放在这儿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:47.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我留宿一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚也没见你通知一声就跑过来  的确很突然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  和哥哥吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没猜错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也来猜一下吵架原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自吃了你期待已久的在车站前转角处那家店买的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸如此类…的…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情我就不问了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不用勉强她说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家家都有难念的经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先跟家人联系下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计她什么也没说就直接跑过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物里的怨气还真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可怕可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏树君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在冬马在我家  样子有些怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  什么？  是你把那家店的布丁给…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这个没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仔细听好  车站前转角处的那家店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是个布丁也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站前转角处的那家店还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害  很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家店的确很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要小看甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在吃糖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这里「舐める」有双重含义，春香的意思是轻视，夏奈错误理解成舔）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  他想法太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很甜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:52.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（同样这里的「甘い」也有天真和甜两种含义）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马今天就住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡点茶喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  刚刚谈到的车站前转角处那家店的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们家买了三个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事布丁只剩两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有谁来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么原来是健啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是健叔哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  现在没空招呼你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不偶尔露个面  怕你们把血浓于水这档子事给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是见面礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站前转角处那家店的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实之前自己那份有三分之一左右被我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料想到有这事  我也吃了三分之一左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到夏奈在吃  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为那份是夏奈的就把剩下的三分之一也吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是夏奈干的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明留了一些的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你做这些惹人误解的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说一共买了几个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  健叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了  大家吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香都这么说了  快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  既然这样  我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好品尝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她们会很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  乡下老家寄来了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分你们一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们俩是怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说夏奈  分是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是送给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…对了…做成果酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接吃也很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像春香这样熟知苹果的人是知道苹果想变成什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香有些奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…内田你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  内田送来些苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…这样啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田  不好意思你和夏奈玩会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…千秋  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋也有些异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田你来的真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈倒是很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你一路走过来一定累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累的时候应该
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补充糖分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去上个厕所  绝对不能打开那个箱子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…夏奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经警告你不能看了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家兴致勃勃地送过来  我们就高高兴兴地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  都怪我不知情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自责了  怎么说也是礼物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…既然已经被你看到了  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你已经做好心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空着手你也敢来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不带东西就不能来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  内田也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是为了点心才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经吃完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意吃烤苹果的话  春香会给你做一堆的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤苹果吗？赚到了  五六个我都吃的下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  能吃五六个啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田吃了两个就倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  回来了啊  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马怎么了  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是春香给的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这苹果到底有什么含义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是随口说说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  用这个苹果做些能讨冬马欢心的东西怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢  你觉得是哪里出错才会失败呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始做？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香和谁聊电话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以前也见过的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…那个大个子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…的确有这么个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在聊什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树很会做饭  但做甜食却不在行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我就让他去请教春香大师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  春香大师现在正在授业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不对啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:15:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止你见过能让春香如此情绪化的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是喜欢上对方了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾那家伙被我排除在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「春香姐姐可以托付终身的对象」文件夹之外了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有这个决定权吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那文件夹干嘛用的啊  反正肯定是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就会演变成甜的辣的无论什么都为你做的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话家里的三餐就由你来操办了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就为春香姐姐快做好的咖喱添加最后一道工序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是练习做饭如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能与千秋  春香和夏奈相识真是太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬…冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞了半天还是吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  貌似电话还得聊很久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我们来完成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  认真点干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  放些什么配料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些等会再放啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  是鸡蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋去拿鸡蛋来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你等等再放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷包蛋那种就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  鸡蛋要做荷包蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…打碎把蛋黄放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再放砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  放砂糖进去做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才谁说放砂糖进去来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是砂糖是咖喱块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  然后咖喱块呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  刚才有好好搅拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:17:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  把这些装盘放进预热过的烤炉里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  用烤炉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用烤炉干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意是不是太甜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说  我可是按照指示做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放些盐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马把那边的盐递过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马没在那吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终也没做出能吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  肚子饿的话吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻到咖喱味了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吃了我的布丁吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有证据证明这是你的布丁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖子上明明写着名字  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写在那儿  多容易认为是花纹不小心看漏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏树  这就是你的不对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向冬马道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏树你听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回是哥哥做错了  快向冬马道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我错了  再去给你买一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  请让我留宿一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有布丁  吃蛋包饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好教育教育夏树君的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  那是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我去准备做晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那位哥哥说的还真没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  夏奈站在他那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样  名字写得小小的也难怪看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要写就得写的大一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  一百什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数字十加上零就是冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:51.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（冬和十的发音都是トウ，后面的0发音取自圈「ま（る）」也是马的发音）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你是天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我也来做一个  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:21:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加号还有「添加」的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后加上数字「七」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼起来就是  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这么一说啊  你也是天才吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是实际上别人真能看懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  的确是有些微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都听到怎么解读那些了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如去问问春香姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚该怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐能认可  我就认可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也不是很清楚  总之你很臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家多吃点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:22:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你怎么理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百零七？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加起来了  加起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说对了吧  一百零七
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一百零七
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健偶尔也会做件好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让大家高兴我就满意了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你知道那家店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…丽子很喜欢那家店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.78,0:23:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回  南家三姐妹～欢迎回来～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应有的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽子…
